Definition: any of various minerals consisting of hydrous silicates of aluminum or potassium etc. that crystallize in forms that allow perfect cleavage into very thin leaves
Example: used as dielectrics because of their resistance to electricity
Synonyms: adj, pert, micaceous, isinglass, mineral, transparent_substance, any, of, various, minerals, consisting, hydrous, silicates, aluminum, or, potassium, etc, that, crystallize, in, forms, allow, perfect, cleavage, into, very, thin, leaves, used, as, dielectrics, because, their, resistance, to, electricity
Category: noun.substance
